displayProperties.name: Event Information
displayProperties.description:
â€¢ Earn Spectral Pages by completing activities throughout the system with a mask equipped. Launch into the Haunted Sector playlist and defeat Headless Ones to transform Spectral Pages into Manifested Pages. The more Headless Ones that are defeated, the more Spectral Pages can be transformed into Manifested Pages, and the more Festival of the Lost weapons and Candy can be rewarded.

â€¢ Manifested Pages can be redeemed at the Book of the Forgotten, located in the Tower, to unlock legends, stories, and tales of the Tower.

â€¢ Earn Eerie Engrams by completing Haunted Sectors or higher difficulty Haunted Sectors. Eerie Engrams can be decoded as is, or focused into Eerie Exotic Engrams with Eva.

â€¢Earn Candy by defeating combatants and completing activities throughout the system with a mask equipped. Candy can be used to purchase Mystery Grab Bags from Eva, which may contain Masterwork materials. Candy can also be used to purchase masks from Eva.

â€¢ Complete Event Challenges, located on the Quest screen, to acquire cool event rewards!
